---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Thanks - Old World Rankings"
  description="Thanks for signing up to test the OWR mobile apps."
  noindex={true}
>
  <Nav />

  <main class="pt-24 pb-16 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-6 rounded-full bg-owr-gold/20 flex items-center justify-center">
        <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-owr-gold" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-6xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Thank you!</h1>
      <p class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-owr-gold-dark dark:text-owr-gold mb-6">You're on the list.</p>
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-lg mb-4">
        Seriously, thank you for putting your hand up. Beta testers are how this thing actually
        gets good before launch, and we don't take that for granted.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 text-base mb-8">
        Depending on demand we'll be back to you as soon as we can with your TestFlight or Play
        Store invite plus a Discord link for the private testers channel. Hopefully we can get
        everyone in, but if intake fills up we may have to stagger invites. Keep an eye on the
        inbox for the email you signed up with.
      </p>
      <a
        href="/"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-2.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 text-gray-900 dark:text-white font-medium hover:bg-gray-200 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 transition-colors"
      >
        Back to OWR
      </a>
    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
